Program: The Forum
Title: Big Data and Us
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p029y54m
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 10 Nov 2014
From digital exahust to data-brokers, algorithms and data art, who and what can we believe in the world of Big Data? Bridget Kendall asks data researcher Adam Tanner, governance expert Sharath Srinivasan and designer Karin Von Ompteda to dive into the data lake. (Photo: part of a honeycomb data-art installation: ‘Colony’ by David Hedberg and Gabriele Dini) Show less